text: This morning - on the first anniversary of his confirmation - Secretary Tillerson briefed us on the @StateDept's work. I am glad to have this TX-26 constituent at the helm of our nation's diplomacy.

I appreciate the time people have taken to reach out to myself and other GOP Members involved in the train accident this morning. Today is a tragic day for those who were hurt. Please continue to pray for victims and their families.

Statement from Dr. Burgess’ Spokesperson Emma Thomson: “I have spoken to Dr. Burgess and thankfully he was not injured in the train accident. Following the accident, he helped to administer aid to victims - like he does during any emergency. We hope to share more info soon."
